#~ msgid ""
#~ "Currently, due to stream resource "
#~ "constraint, we can only support a "
#~ "few buckets in piecewise graph mode "
#~ "now, which will cause redundant "
#~ "computing and may lead to performance"
#~ " degradation compared with eager mode."
#~ msgstr "目前，由于流资源限制，分段计算图模式仅支持少量桶，这会导致冗余计算，与 eager 模式相比可能带来性能下降。"

#~ msgid "How is it implemented?"
#~ msgstr "它是如何实现的？"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "When using piecewise graph, we just "
#~ "need to follow the above-mentioned "
#~ "process. But when in full graph, "
#~ "due to the complexity of the "
#~ "attention, sometimes we need to update"
#~ " attention op's params before execution."
#~ " So we implement `update_attn_params` and"
#~ " `update_mla_attn_params` functions for full "
#~ "graph mode. During forward, memory will"
#~ " be reused between different ops, so"
#~ " we can't update attention op's "
#~ "params before forward. In ACL Graph, "
#~ "we use `torch.npu.graph_task_update_begin` and "
#~ "`torch.npu.graph_task_update_end` to do it, "
#~ "and use `torch.npu.ExternalEvent` to ensure"
#~ " order between param updates and op"
#~ " executions."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "使用分段计算图时，只需遵循上述流程。但在完整计算图模式下，由于注意力机制的复杂性，有时需要在执行前更新注意力算子的参数。因此，我们为完整计算图模式实现了"
#~ " `update_attn_params` 和 `update_mla_attn_params` "
#~ "函数。在前向传播过程中，不同算子之间会复用内存，因此无法在前向传播之前更新注意力算子的参数。在 ACL "
#~ "计算图中，我们使用 `torch.npu.graph_task_update_begin` 和 "
#~ "`torch.npu.graph_task_update_end` 来实现此功能，并使用 "
#~ "`torch.npu.ExternalEvent` 来确保参数更新与算子执行之间的顺序。"

#~ msgid "DFX"
#~ msgstr "DFX"

#~ msgid "Stream resource constraint"
#~ msgstr "流资源限制"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Currently, we can only capture 1800 "
#~ "graphs at most, due to the "
#~ "limitation of ACL graph that a "
#~ "graph requires at least a separate "
#~ "stream. This number is bounded by "
#~ "the number of streams, which is "
#~ "2048; we save 248 streams as a "
#~ "buffer. Besides, there are many "
#~ "variables that can affect the number "
#~ "of buckets:"
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "目前，由于 ACL 计算图要求每个图至少需要一个独立的流，我们最多只能捕获 1800 "
#~ "个计算图。此数量受限于流的总数（2048 个），我们保留了 248 "
#~ "个流作为缓冲区。此外，还有许多变量会影响桶的数量："

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Piecewise graph divides the model into"
#~ " `num_hidden_layers + 1` sub modules, "
#~ "based on the attention layer. Every "
#~ "sub module is a single graph which"
#~ " needs to cost a stream, so the"
#~ " number of buckets in piecewise graph"
#~ " mode is very tight compared with "
#~ "full graph mode."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "分段计算图根据注意力层将模型划分为 `num_hidden_layers + 1` "
#~ "个子模块。每个子模块是一个独立的计算图，需要消耗一个流，因此与完整计算图模式相比，分段计算图模式下的桶数量非常紧张。"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "The number of streams required for "
#~ "a graph is related to the number"
#~ " of comm domains. Each comm domain"
#~ " will increase one stream consumed by"
#~ " a graph."
#~ msgstr "计算图所需的流数量与通信域的数量相关。每个通信域会增加计算图消耗的一个流。"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "When multi-stream is explicitly called"
#~ " in a sub module, it will "
#~ "consume an additional stream."
#~ msgstr "当在子模块中显式调用多流时，会额外消耗一个流。"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "There are some other rules about "
#~ "ACL Graph and stream. Currently, we "
#~ "use func `update_aclgraph_sizes` to calculate"
#~ " the maximum number of buckets and"
#~ " update `graph_batch_sizes` to ensure "
#~ "stream resource is sufficient."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "关于 ACL 计算图和流还有一些其他规则。目前，我们使用 `update_aclgraph_sizes`"
#~ " 函数来计算最大桶数量并更新 `graph_batch_sizes`，以确保流资源充足。"

#~ msgid "We will expand the stream resource limitation in the future."
#~ msgstr "未来我们将放宽流资源的限制。"

#~ msgid "Limitations"
#~ msgstr "限制"

#~ msgid "`FULL` and `FULL_AND_PIECEWISE` are not supported now;"
#~ msgstr "目前不支持 `FULL` 和 `FULL_AND_PIECEWISE`；"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "When use ACL Graph and MTP and "
#~ "`num_speculative_tokens > 1`, as vLLM "
#~ "don't support this case in v0.11.0, "
#~ "we need to set `cudagraph_capture_sizes` "
#~ "explicitly."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "当使用 ACL 计算图和 MTP 且 "
#~ "`num_speculative_tokens > 1` 时，由于 vLLM 在"
#~ " v0.11.0 版本中不支持此场景，需要显式设置 `cudagraph_capture_sizes`。"

#~ msgid "`use_inductor` is not supported now;"
#~ msgstr "目前不支持 `use_inductor`；"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "When in graph mode, vLLM will call"
#~ " `current_platform.get_static_graph_wrapper_cls` to get"
#~ " the current device's graph model "
#~ "wrapper, so what we need to do "
#~ "is implement the graph mode wrapper "
#~ "on Ascend: `ACLGraphWrapper`."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "在计算图模式下，vLLM 会调用 "
#~ "`current_platform.get_static_graph_wrapper_cls` "
#~ "获取当前设备的计算图模型包装器，因此我们需要在 Ascend "
#~ "上实现计算图模式包装器：`ACLGraphWrapper`。"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "vLLM has added `support_torch_compile` "
#~ "decorator to all models. This decorator"
#~ " will replace the `__init__` and "
#~ "`forward` interface of the model class."
#~ " When `forward` is called, the code"
#~ " inside the `ACLGraphWrapper` will be "
#~ "executed, and it will do capture "
#~ "or replay as mentioned above."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "vLLM 已为所有模型添加了 `support_torch_compile` "
#~ "装饰器。该装饰器会替换模型类的 `__init__` 和 `forward` 接口。当调用"
#~ " `forward` 时，将执行 `ACLGraphWrapper` "
#~ "内的代码，并根据上述说明进行捕获或回放。"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "The attention backends that implement "
#~ "`update_graph_params()` are `PagedAttention` and "
#~ "`BlockManagerAttention`."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "实现 `update_graph_params()` 的注意力后端是 `PagedAttention`"
#~ " 和 `BlockManagerAttention`。"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "The current implementation uses a "
#~ "synchronous update pattern: the host "
#~ "waits for the update stream to "
#~ "finish before replay begins. This is "
#~ "simpler to reason about and sufficient"
#~ " for current workloads. An asynchronous "
#~ "pattern that overlaps update with replay"
#~ " is possible in principle but not "
#~ "yet implemented."
#~ msgstr "当前实现使用同步更新模式：主机等待更新流完成后再开始重放。这样更容易推理，并且对于当前工作负载来说已经足够。异步模式在原则上可以重叠更新和重放，但尚未实现。"

#~ msgid "Piecewise graph capture and replay"
#~ msgstr "分段图捕获与重放"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Piecewise mode captures each model layer"
#~ " as a separate ACL graph. This "
#~ "reduces per-graph memory pressure and"
#~ " makes it feasible to capture larger"
#~ " batch sizes on Ascend. The trade-"
#~ "off is that each layer incurs a"
#~ " replay launch, so the host overhead"
#~ " saved by graph mode is partially "
#~ "offset by the number of segments."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "分段模式将每个模型层捕获为单独的 ACL 计算图。这减少了每个计算图的内存压力，使得在 Ascend"
#~ " 上捕获更大的批次大小成为可能。代价是每层都会产生一次重放启动，因此计算图模式节省的主机开销会被分段数量部分抵消。"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Piecewise capture is implemented in "
#~ "`vllm_ascend.compilation.acl_graph.ACLGraphWrapper._capture_piecewise()`."
#~ " The wrapper iterates over the model"
#~ " layers, captures each one individually,"
#~ " and stores the resulting graph "
#~ "handles in a list. During replay, "
#~ "`_replay_piecewise()` replays each segment in"
#~ " order."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "分段捕获在 "
#~ "`vllm_ascend.compilation.acl_graph.ACLGraphWrapper._capture_piecewise()`"
#~ " 中实现。封装器遍历模型层，单独捕获每一层，并将生成的计算图句柄存储在列表中。在重放期间，`_replay_piecewise()`"
#~ " 按顺序重放每个段。"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Piecewise mode does not require the "
#~ "host-side attention parameter update "
#~ "mechanism described above, because each "
#~ "layer's graph is small enough that "
#~ "the attention parameters are captured as"
#~ " part of the graph itself."
#~ msgstr "分段模式不需要上述的主机端注意力参数更新机制，因为每层的计算图足够小，注意力参数可以作为计算图本身的一部分被捕获。"

#~ msgid "Graph pool management"
#~ msgstr "计算图池管理"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "ACL graph capture requires a memory "
#~ "pool that persists across captures. The"
#~ " pool is created once during the "
#~ "first capture and reused for subsequent"
#~ " captures of the same batch "
#~ "descriptor. The pool is destroyed when"
#~ " the `ACLGraphWrapper` is garbage collected"
#~ " or when the model is reloaded."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "ACL 计算图捕获需要一个跨捕获持久化的内存池。该池在第一次捕获期间创建一次，并用于同一批次描述符的后续捕获。当 "
#~ "`ACLGraphWrapper` 被垃圾回收或模型重新加载时，该池被销毁。"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "The pool is managed by "
#~ "`torch.npu.graph_pool_handle()` and "
#~ "`torch.npu.graph_pool_handle_destroy()`. The current "
#~ "implementation creates one pool per "
#~ "batch descriptor, which is sufficient "
#~ "for the typical number of capture "
#~ "sizes. If the number of capture "
#~ "sizes grows significantly, pool memory "
#~ "may become a concern."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "该池由 `torch.npu.graph_pool_handle()` 和 "
#~ "`torch.npu.graph_pool_handle_destroy()` "
#~ "管理。当前实现为每个批次描述符创建一个池，这对于典型的捕获大小数量来说已经足够。如果捕获大小数量显著增长，池内存可能会成为一个问题。"

#~ msgid "Error handling and fallback"
#~ msgstr "错误处理与回退"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "If ACL graph capture fails for any"
#~ " reason (e.g., out of memory, stream"
#~ " resource exhaustion, unsupported operator), "
#~ "the wrapper falls back to eager "
#~ "execution for that batch descriptor. The"
#~ " failure is logged but does not "
#~ "crash the model. Subsequent requests for"
#~ " the same batch descriptor will "
#~ "attempt capture again, which may succeed"
#~ " if the resource situation has "
#~ "changed."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "如果 ACL "
#~ "计算图捕获因任何原因失败（例如，内存不足、流资源耗尽、不支持的算子），封装器会为该批次描述符回退到立即执行模式。失败会被记录，但不会导致模型崩溃。后续对同一批次描述符的请求将再次尝试捕获，如果资源情况已发生变化，则可能成功。"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Similarly, if replay fails (e.g., due"
#~ " to a device error), the wrapper "
#~ "falls back to eager execution for "
#~ "that request and logs the error. "
#~ "The graph is not evicted from the"
#~ " cache on replay failure, because the"
#~ " failure may be transient."
#~ msgstr "类似地，如果重放失败（例如，由于设备错误），封装器会为该请求回退到立即执行模式并记录错误。重放失败时不会从缓存中驱逐该计算图，因为失败可能是暂时的。"

